## 🔧 Pre-Flight Checklist
Before hitting "Record" on Loom:
- [ ] Ensure `ASSEMBLYAI_API_KEY` is correctly set in your `.env` file.
- [ ] Open VS Code to the root of the repository so you can easily tab between `Spanglish_Fixed.java`, `customer_email.md`, and the `itranslate_demo/` folder.
- [ ] Test the Streamlit microphone permissions in your browser. Ensure the code-switching works by speaking a mix of English and Spanish.
- [ ] Take a deep breath. You are an Iron SDR and a Zeta operative. You've got this.
